}</ref>、[[NIGHTMARE_(樂隊)|惡夢]]、[[Kagrra,|Kagrra,]]、[[the_GazettE|the GazettE]]<ref name="Nightmare,Akiya&Gazette">{{cite web|title=LUNA SEA: The Lasting Legacy|url=http://jrockrevolution.com/2007/08/webzine/luna-sea-the-lasting-legacy-24|work=JRock Revolution|date=2007-08-25|accessdate=2013-02-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011233617/http://jrockrevolution.com/2007/08/webzine/luna-sea-the-lasting-legacy-24|archivedate=2014-10-11}}</ref>。{{link-ja|Kra|Kra}}的鼓手靖乃表示，他是因為真矢而開始打鼓。該樂團的前任吉他手{{link-ja|舞 (音樂人)|まい|舞}}是SUGIZO和INORAN的樂迷<ref>{{cite web|title=Kra Interview!|url=http://jrockrevolution.com/2008/04/webzine/kra-interview-235|work=JRock Revolution|date=2008-04-26|accessdate=2013-02-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011233213/http://jrockrevolution.com/2008/04/webzine/kra-interview-235|archivedate=2014-10-11}}</ref>。[[Versailles_-Philharmonic_Quintet-|凡爾賽宮]]的成員透露，他們受到月之海和X JAPAN的影響最大。主唱[[KAMIJO|KAMIJO]]表示：「我認為日本音樂界中，沒有任何人不受他們影響」<ref>{{cite web|title=Descendants of Roses: Versailles Interview Part 2|url=http://jrockrevolution.com/2008/03/webzine/descendants-of-roses-versailles-interview-part-2-227|work=JRock Revolution|date=2008-03-06|accessdate=2014-12-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107165558/http://jrockrevolution.com/2008/03/webzine/descendants-of-roses-versailles-interview-part-2-227|archivedate=2014-11-07}}</ref>。同樣，[[Galneryus|GALNERYUS]]和{{link-ja|DELUHI|DELUHI}}的吉他手[[Leda|Leda]]也也表示：「以前原本對音樂沒有特別興趣，直到有個朋友給我聽了X JAPAN和月之海」<ref>{{cite web|title=Interview: DELUHI |url=http://jrockrevolution.com/2009/05/webzine/interview-deluhi-269 |work=JRock Revolution |date=2009-05-14 |accessdate=2013-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011233510/http://jrockrevolution.com/2009/05/webzine/interview-deluhi-269 |archivedate=2014-10-11 }}</ref>。{{link-ja|DuelJewel|DuelJewel}}的主唱隼人和吉他手祐彌表示，月之海是他們加入視覺系運動的主因<ref>{{cite web|title=YOU Interview the Artists: DuelJewel|url=http://jrockrevolution.com/2007/10/webzine/you-i